2015-03-18
    * 0.2.0 release
    * Support disable and removal nscd package.
    * Enable parameters in the main nscd::init class.
    * Add more rspec tests.

2014-12-09
    * 0.1.0 release
    * Support to enable and configure paranoia mode.
    * Support to configure service cache.
    * Support to configure number of threads
    * Fixes for puppet3.

2012-05-21  Steve Traylen  <steve.traylen@cern.ch
    * 0.0.1 release

